title: BreakBox 3D arcade game 1.03
description:
Break all bricks with the ball!!!

Beware of: 
- lava floor brick (-1 point) 
- black floor holes (sudden death)

ADJUSTABLE zero position of the device, just touch the red arrow-cross at the bottom left corner of the screen as playing

Bricks:
- red +1 point
- dark blue +2 points
- gold +5
- bomb +3 and + neighbour's points
- pink makes 2-4 new bricks, red, dark blue or gold
- light blue 10-1, be QUICK and hit it as soon as possible

Complete all level pages, collect a minimum of 64 stars and unlock next level page

GOOD LUCK!
